data.title: Igersheim - Classical Singing Competition DEBUT
data.meta_description: This competition would like to have an important placement in the Competition world of Young singers. Debut is a Competition which has a bride spectrum of special ways of preparation of young singers in the Music world. The Young singers have optimal opportunities to take part in our competiton, because we can use the location of Jeunesses Musicales Academy at the Castle of Weikersheim. They are completely supplied with food and lodging.
data.text:

The Young singers have optimal opportunities to take part in our competiton, because we can use the location of Jeunesses Musicales Academy at the Castle of Weikersheim. They are completely supplied with food and lodging.
